# RapidAid Analytics Dashboard UI Design

## Purpose

The Analytics Dashboard provides insights into emergency response performance, hospital utilization, ambulance operations, and system usage. It helps administrators and decision-makers monitor the effectiveness of the RapidAid platform.

## Page Layout

### Header

- 🚑 RapidAid Logo
- Dashboard
- Reports
- Analytics
- Notifications
- Settings
- Logout

---

## Dashboard Overview

Display KPI Cards:

- 🚨 Total Emergency Requests
- 🚑 Active Ambulances
- 🏥 Registered Hospitals
- 👥 Total Registered Users
- ⏱️ Average Response Time
- ✅ Successful Emergency Responses

